Main responsibilities:
1. Technical supplier development: lead the price evaluation of non-standard automated equipment suppliers;
2. Supply chain resilience construction: establish a dual-source supply system for key components and design chain breakage emergency plans;
3. Technical risk pre-control: monitor technical iteration risks and implement technical confidentiality management;
4. Be responsible for the recruitment, training and performance appraisal of the supplier management team to improve the overall technical level and work efficiency of the team.

